name: Protocol Net Gain
description: Protocol Net Gain ($PNG) is an innovative Solana-based token designed to create an engaging and dynamic ecosystem for traders. It incorporates an AI-managed buyback and burn mechanism to enhance scarcity and optimize market conditions. Each transaction incurs a 10% fee, which is converted into SOL and stored in an escrow wallet. The AI algorithm strategically executes buybacks and burns based on trading volumes, ensuring a sustainable and adaptive token economy. Additionally, the development team retains a 9.99% supply share and a 1% fixed fee from transactions to support ongoing project growth and innovation.
